      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chicken thighs</strong> to an<strong> oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong>, <strong>capers</strong>, <strong>black olives</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic, bay leaves</strong> and 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>to the dish with the <strong>chicken thighs</strong></p>",
